<br>
These games are really about your ability to make friends online, and how to interact with them. If you are not capable of handling people very well, then ya many of these games are really gonna suck. Your gonna be the lfg guy all nite. <br>
I say when picking a game, pick the one with most of your friends play or people you know play. And if you need a break, take one. <br>
