<br>
1. You don't really get a full feeling of what your class can really do until after the first ten levels or so. Since you can't actually become fully fledged in your class until you get level 5, grouping at early levels 1-8 or 1-10 or so can be a little annoying but those levels really don't take long anyway.<br>
<br>
